12.5 Questions. Episode 1. 
Evgenya is her name. Making drinks Greater is her game. She’s the newest component to our Greater equation. The rest is answered in these 12.5 questions. Tune in!

*Coconut Basil Highball*

- Greater Than: 50ml
- Lime Juice: 10ml
- Basil leaves: a handful tapped & dropped 
- Coconut Water to top off

*Add a touch of honey for additional sweetness 

Method: Combine all ingredients in a tall glass over ice cubes. Garnish with a fresh basil sprig.

latestPosts.caption:
Juniper Bomb doesn’t do regular. Only BOMB.
Here’s cocktail #1 from the Bomb Recipe Series: the Bomb Shandy.

With 3X the flavour, 3X the chaos and 3X the glitch.
Just like the gin.

💣 Here’s how you can make yours:

- Pour 30ml Orange Juice in a highball glass
- Mix 90ml Ginger Beer into it
- Fill a shot glass with 30ml Juniper Bomb
- Place it on the chopsticks on top of the highball glass 
- Punch the table and drop it into the drink!

Juniper Bomb might’ve been born from an accident, but these two photos being slightly different? That was on purpose.

Spot all the differences in the images, leave an emoji of your choice in the comments below and DM your answer to us to win a bottle of this electric gin!

📍 Available in select cities in Maharashtra, Goa & Haryana. Not in these states? Ask a friend to do the spotting.

#JuniperBombGin #Giveaway #SpotTheDifference

Usually not in the dark.

This isn’t your average gin. It’s your gin, turned 3 times up. Exploding with 3X the Juniper and 3X the Flavour!

Now in Goa, Maharashtra and Haryana at a store near you.
